emp_mlo_reclaim_ducal_lands_desc:0 "Montferrat occupies Novara and Pavia, cities which should by right belong to Milan, having been included in the boundaries of the Duchy as defined in the imperial diploma of 1395. If we are to return to our former strength, we must retake these cities!"
emp_mlo_control_the_vatican_desc:0 "For too long have the Saracens to our south occupied the holy city of Rome. We must retake the city and restore the Pope to his rightful position."